surely if you are in a low power zone and things are slow sow all you want to.  even sow yourself.  MY POINT is, as i shall spell it out for you lacking the adequate comprehension ability, is that in high power zone cases the MANA is important, not the BUFF.<BR>
<BR>
buffs are excellent in cases when buffing stations can be set up against a single powerful mob like a dragon.  they are a power drain when mana must be constantly spent keeping people alive, or keeping people rezzed.  think about it.<BR>
