				Has anyone bothered to Test the 4 additional AC over SoW?  To be honest, I don't generally cast SoW on Wizzies.  Main tanks and Myself as a timer.  At 51, Full round of buffs Reso/SoW/Pinz, gets me through 5ppl and I am oom.  207 wis and 60 in mana gear (keep losing the damn rolls on BP's) Effectively I have 2200 mana.  Takes at least 10 minutes to med back to full.  If I skip the casters on SOW then Pulling can start immediately, 900 mana down for myself and 2 tanks plus reso's on all and all pinz'd, leaves me at about 20 mana.  By the time they have INC I am up to 30 and smooth sailing from there.  Keeping it speedy is a good idea, otherwise you spend all your time buffing.  Besides, most casters don't ask for SoW once you tell them how much it costs hehe.
